tid":1941282,"uid":43751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:38:43.000Z","msg":"花木蘭都只係胡人<br />\n只有歸化左中原既塞內胡人 先會打外族胡人<br />\n<br />\n本土 華夏 只係耕田既奴隸 唔識打仗<br />\n要靠入籍兵"},{"pid":"9664845121de809059f3467298b57f0ac7017d33","tid":1941282,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"支那菲不嬲都係搵著數嘅雞黎架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前同條泡菜仔一齊添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你估佢真係咁愛支咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},{"pid":"5090f576c4f1ab316c916dc64bd72e50cf040424","tid":1941282,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"花木蘭好似係中亞高加索人<br />\n<br />\n都唔係華人來啦"},{"pid":"e5e5f6b90def352ac7433db9c5361b42d6a8a9da","tid":1941282,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"【幫推thx】和你登記做選民 &amp; 立會要初選「三不投」聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1940443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1940443</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6104d45695ab9866cf2d12434f381a07fa4c4256","tid":1941282,"uid":205160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"香網民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa60d89d99387f69f636d74c67cd9a8eebd076fe","tid":1941282,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:42:26.000Z","msg":"劉亦菲真係同小龍女冇分別，完全唔知外面係點"},{"pid":"9b995bead7650ad229f54aa8e0cf6940677719d2","tid":1941282,"uid":337454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:46:43.000Z","msg":"大把小粉紅屌話係美國人幫美帝賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gi